PART 6: QUANTUM TOURNAMENT — COMPLEX PERMANENT
  Replace T[i][j] with z[i][j] = T[i][j] * e^{i*theta}
  Quantum H = permanent of amplitude matrix
  Connection to BosonSampling
======================================================================

